snippet.title: Game & Watch - Mickey & Donald (c)1982 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This is another one that was emulated almost 2 years ago at this point, but for which I had no video up here.  Thanks to digshadow and Olivier Galibert for the work on this one.  This one is interesting in that it's the only Mickey Mouse / Disney licensed G&W unit that didn't have a more generic / Nintendo IP counterpart.

Game & Watch artwork for MAME was done by DarthMarino (more recently emulated units) and hydef (units emulated before 2020)
https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY  DarthMarino 
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5 hydef
